data.description: Looking to move in before Christmas? Welcome to Coronado Ranch. This beautiful, move in ready home has semi-custom architecture, sophisticated luxury finishes accentuating a thoughtful open floor plan! A special feature of this 4 bedroom, 4 bathroom enclave is the 3rd floor Guest Suite that includes its own living room, bedroom and bathroom with double sinks, and a second floor open den, currently a convenient office space. From the chef’s kitchen with double ovens, quartz island, commercial grade oversized refrigerator, and the technology and lighting package with Bose surround sound and theater speakers, to the covered patio, garden, and manicured landscaping, this home impresses in every way, a gorgeous show home. Over $130k in upgrades makes this masterpiece a work of art with the latest in technology. Ask me for the upgrades sheet. 2643sq. ft, 2 car garage. Price improved for quick sale, Don’t miss this beauty!
